────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

本项目使用了以下开源数据/工具，致谢：

* UCI Machine Learning Repository - Beijing PM2.5 Dataset (2010-2014)
  Liang, X., et al. (2015). Assessing Beijing's PM2.5 pollution.

* OpenAQ Open Air Quality Platform
  https://openaq.org

* PyTorch / scikit-learn / XGBoost / LightGBM / Streamlit
  各自遵循其原始许可证

* GB 3095-2012 《环境空气质量标准》(中国国家标准)
* WHO Global Air Quality Guidelines (2021)
* ASHRAE Standard 55-2020 Thermal Environmental Conditions
